1. *Moraćeš* da se prilagodiš novoj situaciji. (You will have to adjust to the new situation.)

2. On *moraće* da plati visoku cenu. (He will have to pay a high price.)

3. *Moraćeš* da završiš svoj zadatak. (You will have to finish your task.)

4. Oni *moraće* da prihvate izazov. (They will have to accept the challenge.)

5. *Moraćeš* da odabereš pravi put. (You will have to choose the right path.)